item.title: CVE-2017-16125|2024-08-05T20:13:07.211Z -- hackerone -- rtcmulticonnection-client%20node%20module
item.description: rtcmulticonnection-client is a signaling implementation for RTCMultiConnection.js, a multi-session manager. rtcmulticonnection-client is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
